long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is a powerfull yet simple tool to help you to perform your on page SEO analysis.
With this extension you'll be able to analyse:

1. Keyword Presence over different parts of the page
2. Scrap your competitors Headers
3. Highlight different types of links
4. Have quick shortcuts for important sites to analyze your performance.
